snippet.title: Diabotical - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Download now for free - https://www.epicgames.com/store/en-US/product/diabotical/home

Diabotical is out now! Show off your FPS skills and creative game play in this fast paced free-to-play arena shooter. Take to battle with a variety of weapons across 15 different game modes and 30 maps in the eggbot universe.
